-- Great-West Must Repay London Life Policyholders C$456 Million, Judge Says
-- B y   J o e   S c h n e i d e r
-- 2010-10-01T21:45:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-01/great-west-must-repay-london-life-policyholders-c-456-million-judge-says.html
Great-West Lifeco Inc. must repay
London Life Insurance policy holders C$456 million for
improperly using money in their accounts to help pay for a 1997
takeover of the company, an Ontario judge ruled.  To contact the reporter on this story:
